    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>From the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href='http://www.gpo.gov'>www.gpo.gov</a>]By Mr. KING of Iowa:H.R. 1746.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:This legislation contains a clarification that is intendedto limit the scope of an existing statute. As such, this billmakes specific changes to existing law in a manner thatreturns power to the States and to the People, in accordancewith Amendment X of the United States Constitution.[Page H2154]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
    <summaries>
